  <li>Determine and predict costs associated with current and future cloud workloads</li>
  <li>Use strategies and best practices to reduce AWS costs</li>
  <li>Use AWS tools to manage, monitor, alert, and optimize your AWS spend</li>
  <li>Apply strategies to monitor service costs and usage</li>
  <li>Implement governance standards, including resource tagging, account structure, provisioning, permissions, and access.</li>
</ul>

